overview: Rosanna, a rock star, has not been able to find a man who can match her sexual appetite. On the way to a performance, she and her virginal secretary run into Lord Edward of Willoughby, the owner of a mysterious mansion where they will meet some hooded guys, the Lord's hot chauffeur and his lustful female servants, all ready and willing to enjoy the most sexually rewarding evening Rosanna could ever imagine.
title: Anal Manor
